{"tid":1597681,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"大家燒旗還燒旗 唔該燒得有氣勢少少","createTime":"2019-09-27T05:04:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T08:13:10.000Z","uid":209097,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7049361ad18b9037cc572166869b507575b0da82","tid":1597681,"uid":209097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T05:04:14.000Z","msg":"大家之前燒旗就真係齋燒 拆支旗 放落地下點火 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xy7YRr3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXy7YRr3.jpg&h=7739c28d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但咁嘅話其實唔太型 火勢又唔大 唔講以為煲緊蠟咋<br />\n<br />\n所以建議大家一係燒之前就淋火酒 汽油之類 擺埋隻小熊維尼喺上面 然後點著支火柴扔落好 好似Joker燒錢咁 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cJVWDat.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcJVWDat.png&h=29dd7ba5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又或者燒緊嗰陣升起佢 甚至遊街示眾 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/czhepQT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FczhepQT.jpg&h=68780995&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JqLcbvU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJqLcbvU.jpg&h=1660a54b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁嘅話實有畫面過放喺地下尻燒"},{"pid":"2e522e159b307848771e0568bae52c30a6fb00a0","tid":1597681,"uid":209097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T05:04:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"055893910c98f390f46599a27a0cee0f8a7c71d0","tid":1597681,"uid":140793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T05:13:32.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />揸住嚟燒有氣勢啲"},{"pid":"437d217c5801da107a651b6308412280d535e400","tid":1597681,"uid":209097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T05:14:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3cdd6d1e0b9703d5cd6adfd424013033cdeb66d0","tid":1597681,"uid":209097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T05:26:54.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj